  "revision_instructions": [
    "Replace generic bullet points with those in 'bullet_point_rewrites'.",
    "Include more keywords from the job post to improve ATS matching.",
    "Reformat section headers for clarity (e.g., 'Experience' > 'Professional Experience')."
  ],
  "email_summary": "Hi [Candidate Name],\n\nI've reviewed your resume against the Grab job posting. Below are some specific improvements you can make to better align with the role:\n\n- Rewrote several bullet points to highlight measurable impact.\n- Mapped key job description terms to your revised content for better ATS visibility.\n- Suggested formatting and tone changes to reflect Grab’s style.\n\nLet me know if you’d like help applying these edits!\n\nBest,\n[Your AI Resume Assistant]"
}
